flowchart TD
  A[Request verification or reset] --> B[Generic response]
  B --> C{Eligible active or pending user?}
  C -->|no| D[Audit suppressed without email]
  C -->|yes| E[Store hashed single-use token]
  E --> F[Send Resend email]
  F --> G[Confirm token]
  G --> H{Token valid, fresh, unused?}
  H -->|no| I[Reject and audit]
  H -->|yes verification| J[Activate pending_verification user]
  H -->|yes reset| K[Rotate credential and revoke sessions]
